#: .\templates\core\home.html:126
msgid ""
"Bunyodkor Industrial Technopark is a modern industrial zone located in Koson "
"district. The technopark was established to support industrial development, "
"attract investments, and create new jobs. The territory covers 60 hectares "
"and hosts various manufacturing projects including textile production, food "
"processing, energy generation, and other industrial activities."
msgstr ""
"Bunyodkor Industrial Texnoparki Koson tumanida joylashgan zamonaviy sanoat "
"hududidir. Texnopark sanoat rivojlanishini qo‘llab-quvvatlash, "
"investitsiyalarni jalb qilish va yangi ish o‘rinlarini yaratish maqsadida "
"tashkil etilgan. Hudud 60 gektarni tashkil etadi va unda to‘qimachilik "
"ishlab chiqarishi, oziq-ovqatni qayta ishlash, energiya ishlab chiqarish "
"hamda boshqa sanoat faoliyatlarini o‘z ichiga olgan turli ishlab chiqarish "
"loyihalari joylashgan."

